_sText:
This is a remake, completely from scratch and from the ground up, of cs_Crackhouse. This is still in a beta phase and has a lot of work left. The lighting and environment still needs to be adjusted, so don't make too much fuss about it.

This project was not done alongside the original creator, but I wouldn't want to take the credit away from creating the map. I did decompile the map for the measurements, though.

Watch this map for more updates, as they may or may not push out quickly.
